org.zaproxy.zap.view.messagelocation

Class MessageLocationProducerFocusListenerAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.zaproxy.zap.view.messagelocation.MessageLocationProducerFocusListenerAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FocusListener, EventListener

    public class MessageLocationProducerFocusListenerAdapter
extends Object
implements FocusListener
    A FocusListener adapter to multiple MessageLocationProducerFocusListeners.

    Used to listen to changes in the focus of MessageLocationProducers and propagate the event with the custom format.

    Since:
    2.4.0
    See Also:
    FocusListener, MessageLocationProducer, MessageLocationProducerFocusListener
